== 争議 ==
=== 有人懷疑與[[肥胖症|肥胖症]]的关联 ===
自21世纪初，一直有人批评快餐的[[動物福利|動物福利]]纪录，与[[肥胖症|肥胖症]]的关联，以及对环境的影响<ref>{{cite news|last=Barnett|first=Michael|title=Colonel Sanders' new modern army of outlets|url=http://www.marketingweek.co.uk/colonel-sanders-new-modern-army-of-outlets/3021690.article|accessdate=2013-02-11|newspaper=Marketing Week|date=2010-12-16|archive-date=2013-05-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130509023417/http://www.marketingweek.co.uk/colonel-sanders-new-modern-army-of-outlets/3021690.article|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

[[埃里克·施洛瑟|埃里克·施洛瑟]]（{{lang|en|Eric Schlosser}}）于2002年的著作《[[快餐帝国|快餐帝国]]》（{{lang|en|''Fast Food Nation''}}），以及[[摩根·史柏路克|摩根·史柏路克]]于2004年执导并主演的《[[超码的我|超码的我]]》则反映了这些顾虑<ref name="autogenerated26"/>。

=== 是否善待动物  ===
自2003年以来，[[善待动物组织|善待动物组织]]抗议肯德基在世界各地所选择的家禽供应商<ref>{{cite book |author=Yaziji, Michael; Doh, Jonathan |title=NGOs and Corporations: Conflict and Collaboration |series=Business, Value Creation, and Society |chapter=Case illustration: PETA and KFC |pages=112–114 |year=2009 |publisher=Cambridge University Press |isbn=978-0-521-86684-2}}</ref>。

例外的是加拿大肯德基，其签署了一份协议，承诺只选择“善待动物”的供应商。<ref name="WilliamsChampion2011">{{cite book|author1=Chuck Williams|author2=Terry Champion|author3=Ike Hall|title=MGMT|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=8GkHKO0T4P8C&pg=PA78|year=2011|publisher=Cengage Learning|isbn=978-0-17-650235-5|page=78|access-date=2014-05-09|archive-date=2014-06-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140627194304/http://books.google.com/books?id=8GkHKO0T4P8C&pg=PA78|dead-url=no}}</ref>善待动物组织举行了数以千计的示威活动。<ref name="WilliamsChampion2011"/>肯德基美国事业部主席格雷格·戴德里克（{{lang|en|Gregg Dedrick}}）指出，善待动物组织误将肯德基归类为家禽生产商，实际上肯德基只是鸡的买家。<ref name="Swann2010">{{cite book|last=Swann|first=Patricia|title=Cases in Public Relations Management|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=uQCogK0r4g4C&pg=PA121|accessdate=2013-09-26|date=April 2010|publisher=Routledge|isbn=978-0-203-85136-4|pages=121–122|archive-date=2013-10-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131009084124/http://books.google.com/books?id=uQCogK0r4g4C&pg=PA121|dead-url=no}}</ref>2008年，百胜表示：“（身为）食品重大买家，（百胜）有机会及责任影响供应给我们的动物被对待的方式。我们十分重视这个责任，并会持续监控供应商<ref name=an08>{{cite book|title=Annual Report|year=2008|publisher=Yum! Brands|location=Louisville|page=52|url=http://yum.com/investors/annualreport/08annualreport/docs/annualReport08.pdf|accessdate=2013-09-27|archive-date=2013-09-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130905061941/http://www.yum.com/investors/annualreport/08annualreport/docs/annualReport08.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>。”

